Despite facing challenges during the {{ill|Nanboku-chō Period|ja|南北朝時代|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nanboku-chō Period|qq=}}, the Ōi Clan remained influential, continuing to expand under the governance of the {{ill|Ashikaga Clan|ja|足利氏|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashikaga Clan|qq=}}. However, their power waned after the defeat during the {{ill|Ōtō Conflict|ja|大塔合戦|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtō Conflict|qq=}}.
